snippet.title: Classroom Antics - Doki Doki Blue Skies Teaser #1 (Sayori's Route)
snippet.description:
Meet Sakurai! It's about time the Doki Doki universe had a teacher - after all, they're in a school! Young, humorous and relatable, you'll see him on each route. The teenage years are never easy, so perhaps he may be able to shed some insight there as well?
